  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8 : \u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0bb4\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Crackdown on eviction protesters: Call for protests in Yall",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "A protest protest has been called for Saturday 23rd tomorrow in Jaffna in protest against the attack in Kalimugat.",
        "Ramalingam Chandrasekaran, Jaffna district organizer of People's Liberation Front, said that the protest will be held at Jaffna Central Bus Station tomorrow Saturday at 1 pm under the theme \"We will strongly condemn the barbaric attack of Ranil-Rajapakshas on Golbase protestors\".",
        "In the media conference held today 22nd Friday at Jaffna Media Center",
        "Tamil Social Democratic Party leader Suku Comrade, Northern Regional Coordinator of Electricity Service Union K. Ilangumaran, Nallur Socialist Youth Sang organizer K. Saravanan, Parutthura Socialist Youth Sang organizer S. Ganesaruban Agiyoor attended and gave a call for this protest.",
        "Troops and policemen entered the Kotakokama area of \u200b\u200bKalimukhatidal and removed the sheds there and attacked the protesters. So this protest has been called to condemn this attack."
      ],
